BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:J2zyYNFxW-kMcE1SpRWUQ
SUMMARY:Interbay Summer Camps- The Little Gym
DTSTAMP:20260327T050348Z
DTSTART:20260401T000000Z
DESCRIPTION:Interbay summer camps are 3 hours of Serious Fun for kiddos 3-1
	0 years of age! Camp consists of 2 hours of gym time\\\, and 1 hour of sna
	cks and craft time. Every week brings a new and exciting theme for your ca
	mper and we always have blocks\\\, books and coloring pages on standby for
	 those campers that need a break. Camps are held Monday-Wednesday from 1-4
	pm. We offer special discounted pricing for members and camp pack purchase
	s. Non member pricing is $75 for a single camp pass. More information on p
	ack pricing can be found via our scannable QR code. Priority registration 
	opens February 1st.\n\nhttps://discovermagnolia.org/event/interbay-summer-
	camps-the-little-gym/2026-04-01/\n\nFrom Discover Magnolia
URL:https://discovermagnolia.org/event/interbay-summer-camps-the-little-gym
	/2026-04-01/
LOCATION:The Little Gym- Interbay\\\, 2213 15th Ave W\\\, Seattle\\\, WA\\\
	, 98119\\\, United States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:discover-magnolia
CATEGORIES:Discover Magnolia
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT24H
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:y_t40AFAqYXW2G3SBsSr8
SUMMARY:Easter Celebration
DTSTAMP:20260327T050348Z
DTSTART:20260405T100000Z
DESCRIPTION:Please plan to join MUCC on Sunday\\\, April 5th as we celebrat
	e Easter. This will be a joyous celebration with plenty of music and gift 
	bags for the kids and ending with a rousing rendition of the Hallelujah Ch
	orus! The MUCC Children’s Gathering Space will also be open on this Sunday
	 from 9:30 to 11:30 for all kiddos ages 0-5 of families who are attending 
	Worship Services. After Worship\\\, all of the young and young at heart ar
	e invited to the Easter Egg hunt outside and all are invited up to Pilgrim
	 Hall for Fellowship with Mimosas and Hot Cross buns. Invite your family\\
	\, friends\\\, and neighbors to this joyous celebration of hope!\n\nhttps:
	//discovermagnolia.org/event/easter-celebration/\n\nFrom Discover Magnolia
URL:https://discovermagnolia.org/event/easter-celebration/
LOCATION:Magnolia United Church of Christ\\\, 3555 W McGraw St\\\, Seattle\
	\\, WA\\\, 98199\\\, United States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:discover-magnolia
CATEGORIES:Discover Magnolia
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:HM4nScW8eI_qzx5yDhl_V
SUMMARY:Meet Up Magnolia- virtual networking
DTSTAMP:20260327T050348Z
DTSTART:20260409T093000Z
DESCRIPTION:Our member businesses know the value of networking. Join us for
	 our virtual networking event\\\, Meet Up Magnolia\\\, on the  2nd Thursda
	y of every month. \\nHow does this virtual networking work? You simply log
	 on to the Zoom link and will be paired into one-on-one chats for 8 to 10 
	minutes each. We will repeat the process for approximately 3 or 4 rounds. 
	You even have the option to follow up after the meeting and send a message
	 to one or more of the people you meet to keep the dialogue going. \\nSo m
	any people to meet\\\, so many professional relationships to build. Join u
	s HERE.\n\nhttps://discovermagnolia.org/event/meet-up-magnolia-virtual-net
	working-2024-12-12/2026-04-09/\n\nFrom Discover Magnolia
URL:https://discovermagnolia.org/event/meet-up-magnolia-virtual-networking-
	2024-12-12/2026-04-09/
LOCATION:https://us02web.zoom.us/j/85388228818?pwd=amdmUEMvcVo2YjhETkxkbGJC
	a1Q4Zz09
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:discover-magnolia
